    <h1 itemprop="headline" class=" " data-article-head>Earth Day 2024: Urgent need for environmental education in a time of crisis</h1>
        <p class="lead ">We must emphasise the importance of environmental education for a sustainable future</p>
    <hr class="divider">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-5 gn-col-article-meta">
            <div class="article-meta">
        <time class="publish" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2024-04-22T08:00:19+04:00">
    Published:&nbsp;
        <span class="time">April 22, 2024 08:00</span>
    </time>

    <span itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="author">
            <a rel="author" class="font-weight-bold"  itemprop="sameAs" href="#">
                    <span itemprop="name">Ashok Swain, Special to Gulf News</span>
            </a>
    </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-7 gn-col-share d-flex justify-content-start justify-content-md-end">
            <div class="gn-media-follow-us">
                <a  href="javascript:void(0)"
                    class="follow-us-link"
